name: Experiment Or Die #10
description: After a night of drinking and walking from pub to pub in our corrugated Zombie Box Hero suits, my wife had had enough and was ready to go home...but not before we found out who won the costume contest. That was the ONLY reason we were there, because NEITHER of us like to drink. We did end up winning, and despite the prize being some PBR koozies and gift cards to places we don't go...we were still quite happy! In spite of the bird! IG: Nikejerk
